I've been having some major 

trouble downloading MKS Lite and Usi life support for 1.1.2.  I've tried multiple downloads for MKS lite and I only get the tab in the VAB, not the parts. The same goes for usi life support, I can get the physics and effects of it but not the parts. I've seen these models work on YouTube just fine, but they don't work for me.  Can anyone help me figure out how to get these mods to work?

I've had that problem too. I'm not sure how to solve it. Maybe there is a certain folder that needs to be moved.
Same problem, some mods only a few parts show up.

do you have the custom categories? The parts are set to "category = none" usually. I know the Malemute has trouble showing up regardless.

If you have the custom category, check there. Lifesupport recently changed filepaths I believe, maybe some of the parts have the other file paths still. I've spent a good bit of time messing about with RoverDude's mods and they all work (generally speaking) at about a 98.5% success rate, depending on the day of the week and the weather, naturally.

I'd suggest posting a log (preferably output_log.txt) or moving on over to one of RoverDude's threads. Probably get more exposure there.

And be a specific as you can.

Cheers.
